l_cd_analog_record_released_to_commemorate_10_million_views_of_mv" data-image-description="&lt;p>;HIMEHINA (ヒメヒナ)「愛包ダンスホール」MV1000万回再生を記念しCD&#038;レコードが発売へ&lt;/p>;
" data-image-caption="&lt;p>;HIMEHINA (ヒメヒナ)「愛包ダンスホール」MV1000万回再生を記念しCD&#038;レコードが発売へ&lt;/p>;
" data-medium-file="https://p2y.jp/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/himehina_aipai_dance_hall_cd_analog_record_released_to_commemorate_10_million_views_of_mv.jpg" data-large-file="https://p2y.jp/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/himehina_aipai_dance_hall_cd_analog_record_released_to_commemorate_10_million_views_of_mv.jpg" src="https://p2y.jp/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/himehina_aipai_dance_hall_cd_analog_record_released_to_commemorate_10_million_views_of_mv.jpg" alt="HIMEHINA（姬雏）《爱宝舞厅》纪念MV点击量突破1000万次的CD&amp;唱片即将发行" class="wp-image-117121"/><figcaption class="wp-element-caption">图片来源：新闻稿 © 2024 版权所有 2019 Studio LaRa。由 SKIYAKI Inc. 提供支持。</figcaption></figure><p></p><p> 《爱宝舞厅》是作为HIMEHINA第14张单曲发行的歌曲。载歌载舞的视频在 YouTube 等网站上广受欢迎，MV 观看次数超过 1000 万次。 </p><p></p><figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-video is-provider-youtube wp-block-embed-youtube wp-embed-aspect-16-9 wp-has-aspect-ratio"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper"><div class="youtube"><iframe title="HIMEHINA《爱宝舞厅》MV" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/bnofYmfKLeo?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></div></div></figure><p></p><figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-video is-provider-youtube wp-block-embed-youtube wp-embed-aspect-16-9 wp-has-aspect-ratio"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper"><div class="youtube"><iframe title="HIMEHINA《爱宝舞厅》舞蹈视频" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/JWHqBNQL9xQ?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></div></div></figure><p></p><figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-rich is-provider-twitter wp-block-embed-twitter"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper"> https://twitter.com/HimeTanaka_HH/status/1763060679928635872?t=Ckyu4QOWFUD3O_D3d5djnw</div></figure><p></p><p>新发行的HIMEHINA纪念SG《一方/爱宝舞厅》除了《爱宝舞厅》之外，还收录了HIMEHINA的第一首原创歌曲《一方》。双A面单曲将有两种格式：CD 和模拟唱片。 12英寸模拟唱片有一个约30厘米大小的大外套，可以作为室内装饰。</p><p></p><h3 id="outline__1" class="wp-block-heading">产品概要</h3><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img decoding="async" src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/pw/AP1GczN1_bNP6YlXB8mXtzHpqCsLGHrm0nvlLh2Iexu9tdhZhxkeN6bBnhrxe1AHRSpKEDiUwsKKZea9eWjjCGiLQtouU-noKLVbL7XFLw9ZycLlnEZvJ7wgKVp6ujtszf_4aZp1hNVJ3jehu7UlIwiy3ITi=w1097-h1097-s-no-gm" alt=""/><figcaption class="wp-element-caption"> “单曲CD”价格：2,200日元（含税） </figcaption></figure><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img decoding="async" src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/pw/AP1GczOLjcP7H1y-RyRDhUHb4FuHRWAnXRPHK1ZoDbJzk8i_v_zVW5mwAt-DTty34PwJIMX3EVjCvE75GuL8BQ4AHY3oNzVHlMhjiaYzCZ8GGQ8UUX8a03Q0ErktKJO921bdjSRORXNLHOYgopvDH0-4_jon=w1097-h1097-s-no-gm" alt=""/><figcaption class="wp-element-caption"> “模拟唱片（45rpm）”售价：5,500日元（含税）</figcaption></figure><figure class="wp-block-table is-style-stripes"><table><tbody><tr><td>产品名称</td><td>姬雏纪念SG“一方/爱凤舞厅”</td></tr><tr><td>发布日期</td><td>2024 年 6 月 26 日星期三（令和 6）</td></tr><tr><td>内容</td><td>01. 人方<br>02.爱宝舞厅<br>03. 人方 (器乐)<br> 04.爱宝舞厅（​​器乐）</td></tr><tr><td>预约接待</td><td>2024年2月29日星期四 19:00~ 4月14日星期日 23:59<br>产品预订页面：https: <a href="https://bit.ly/3uY6vvF" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">//bit.ly/3uY6vvF</a></td></tr></tbody></table></figure><p></p><h3 id="outline__2" class="wp-block-heading">歌曲详情</h3><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img decoding="async" src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/pw/AP1GczPg0YHDr1D2Lx6H83v7UR4ZHb4K9hGfoPnYifYzjzpwfewIiHEv1dxXtl5PbMTQFgY-zIfEVx6kaYrXEIDrHgotb-3ogMJERbHg1o-emAH_KY-n6b_8ucPUYh0Wv7Bc_7KhpIPy-7hBCbDiJRcea5f9=w587-h587-s-no-gm" alt=""/><figcaption class="wp-element-caption"> <strong>「一方」</strong><br>歌曲：HIMEHINA（田中姬、铃木雏）<br>作词：戈戈<br>作曲/编曲：南田健吾（agehasprings Party）<br><br>音源分发/下载：<br> <a href="https://himehina.lnk.to/hitogata/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">https://himehina.lnk.to/hitogata/</a><br>唱片目录：<br> <a href="https://himehina.jp/musics/9662" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noo